<div style="width: 600px; max-height: 550px; overflow-x: auto;"><h1 class="green b_mar_ten">ASK THE (BOOK) EDITORS</h1>
	<p class="size11"><strong>Room: HALL C (602-603)</strong><em><br/>Start: 2:20PM<br/>End: 3:15PM</em></p><br/>
	<p class="rte">Join novelist <b>Philip Athans</b> as he joins <b>Nina Hess</b> (Editor-in-Chief, Wizards of the Coast) <b>Fleetwood Robbins</b> (Editor, Wizards of he Coast) <b>Jak Koke</b> (Managing Editor, Per Aspera Press) and <b>James Sutter</b> (Editor, Paizo) for a spirited Q&amp;A for aspiring authors of fantasy and science fiction. They will cover such topics as query dos and don'ts, how to write better, how to submit your work, and how to build a career as a novelist.</p></div>